rComments: Without a doubt one of the best profs I've had during my time at Brock. I knew little about the subject matter initially, but now find myself thinking about configurations of nationalism and ethnic diversity in new and developed ways. He is obviously smart, and a talented lecturer, but is also approachable. Take a course with him if you can...
Had this prof for two courses. He is an absolute gem! He knows his stuff and is very approachable. Everything about him is great, definitely take a class with him!!
What a great prof! He is enthusiastic and keeps lectures lively and informative.  Brock should keep this guy around.
Cool young prof.  The content can be pretty dry, but he is clear and fun to listen.  Cute and has style, rare for a pol sci prof.

Pretty good professor, seems like an approachable, easy going person. Found his E.U course at Brock to be dry and boring however. Has a tendancy to go a speak too quickly and overestimate the intelletcual comprehension abilities of his class. I.e uses alot of arcance terminology ect.
